init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the meantime, I ran to my closet and put on a nice seersucker suit...

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Confused, I hung up and walked outside.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He gets out of the car and says "Barack Obama Sir."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The tunnel dropped us off at a private airstrip of sorts.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The chopper took off and I could see the cityscape beneath me as we rose up into the sky.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The chopper flew for a few hours and we floated over a large body of water.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The chopper then began to descend and I could see a small island in the distance.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man brought me down a long hall and into an elevator.
